OL,3,CSunak's Sambas: PM offers apology
OL,4,Cafter 'ruining credibility' of shoe
OL,6,FRishi Sunak has issued a "fulsome
OL,7,Fapology" to fans of Adidas Samba
OL,8,Ftrainers after being accused of
OL,9,Fruining their credibility when he was
OL,10,Fpictured in a pair.
OL,12,FThe prime minister told LBC Radio: he
OL,13,Fhas been wearing the German sportswear
OL,14,Fgiant's classic trainers "for many
OL,15,Fyears".
OL,17,FIn a video posted on social media, `
OL,18,Fwho claimed he is a "longtime devotee"
OL,19,Fof the brand ` was shown wearing the
OL,20,Fwhite trainers during an interview in
OL,21,FDowning Street.
