OL,3,CSunak's Sambas: PM offers apology
OL,4,Cafter 'ruining credibility' of shoe
OL,6,F"The first pair my brother got for me
OL,7,Fmany, many years ago ` my first pair
OL,8,Fof fun Adidas trainers as a Christmas
OL,9,Fpresent. I haven't looked back since.
OL,10,FSo I've been a longtime devotee."
OL,12,FHe added: "That pair (in the video) I
OL,13,Fdid buy, but I've had Adidas trainers
OL,14,Ffor a very long time."
OL,16,FBut Mr Sunak, who has also faced
OL,17,Fquestions about the short length of
OL,18,Fhis trousers, said he is "intrigued
OL,19,Fand amused by the amount of focus on
OL,20,Fwhat I'm wearing".
